data.description: Welcome to this spacious tri-level townhouse located in the desirable and growing Wagon Wheel community. This beautiful 2020-built property features three bedrooms, three and a half bathrooms, a loft/bonus room, and a large deck on the third level. The sellers are including the paid-off Vivant security system equipment.As soon as you walk in, you'll be welcomed to a spacious open concept kitchen and family room. On the second level, there are three bedrooms, including the master suite, and a large size laundry room.Moving up to the third level, you'll find a full bathroom, a spacious loft that can be used as a bonus room, and that leads to an open deck! This gem is in a prime location, within walking distance to the Esplanade and the Collection.
